44:12.681 --> 44:14.083
women's college.

44:16.797 --> 44:19.220
She spent four years there and got a bachelor's 
degree. And then she went to Cornell University,

44:19.240 --> 44:22.665
got a master's degree.

44:25.468 --> 44:32.237
And she was employed at the University of Kentucky 
in the fall of 1920 in the zoology department. And

44:33.779 --> 44:44.053
her teaching specialty was histology and 
embryology,

44:33.779 --> 44:44.053
which worked that she had taken chiefly at 
Cornell.

44:49.703 --> 44:57.614
And we belonged to a group of faculty there that 
socialized and had parties and so forth and so on.

44:57.654 --> 44:58.415
We got acquainted. And we married in 1922.

